This plugin adds the Threat Patrols repository for OPNsense packages.

Threat Patrols plugins include:-

MultiCLOUDsense
Enables running OPNsense on various cloud-compute providers with DevOps automation features.

Configuration Sync
Synchronize system configuration .xml files to various cloud-storage providers.

AutoSSH
Maintain persistent SSH forward/reverse tunnels from OPNsense to remote systems.

WWW: https://documentation.threatpatrols.com/opnsense-plugins/
